            "title": "天文台｜本港今早天氣顯著轉涼 氣溫普遍降至16度左右 日間最高氣溫約20度",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"黎志偉攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/189766c36a35786d1c2021657703b2db/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250329/_2025032906354713394.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">黎志偉攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>一股清勁至強風程度的東北季候風正影響廣東沿岸。同時，一道廣闊雲雨帶正覆蓋華南。本港今早天氣顯著轉涼，氣溫普遍降至16度左右，較昨日低八至十度。\n\n</p>\n<p>本港地區今日天氣預測，多雲，有幾陣雨。早晚清涼。日間最高氣溫約20度。吹和緩至清勁北至東北風，離岸及高地間中吹強風。\n\n</p>\n<p>展望未來兩三日天氣持續清涼，有一兩陣雨，市區最低氣溫在15度左右，新界再低兩三度。下週中後期天色好轉，氣溫逐步回升。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164695/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"分區氣溫\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/78bb55cf54bd0d19f139bde4f21095e7/2025-03/2025-03-29_06_25_47.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        分區氣溫\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164696/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"九天天氣預報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/39588904e0923c092739f6d2047f8b29/2025-03/2025-03-29_06_26_34.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        九天天氣預報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164697/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"本港今早天氣顯著轉涼。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1e90d02fb34bafe85d01a5f387534fdb/2025-03/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-03-29-06-10-49_002.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        本港今早天氣顯著轉涼。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164698/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"氣溫普遍降至16度左右。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1ac7f5fc5cb9089a3140be566ecaf077/2025-03/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-03-29-06-10-57_006.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        氣溫普遍降至16度左右。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164699/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"日間最高氣溫約20度。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ad6c078607025b4f644fc092aa2a3224/2025-03/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-03-29-06-10-55_005.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        日間最高氣溫約20度。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>一股清勁至強風程度的東北季候風會在未來一兩日影響廣東沿岸，該區天氣清涼及有一兩陣雨。隨著季候風逐漸緩和及被一股較乾燥的偏東氣流取代，下週中後期廣東地區天色好轉，氣溫逐步回升，日間溫暖。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
